Source.Contents:
/#
   A type that describes the rate of exchange at which the embedded option in a Dual Currency Deposit has been struck.
 #/
record FpML5.recordkeeping.DualCurrencyStrikePrice {
  # The rate of exchange between the two currencies of the leg of a deal.
  rate : decimal?

  # The method by which the strike rate is quoted, in terms of the deposit (principal) and alternate currencies.
  strikeQuoteBasis : string?

}

rate.Doc: The rate of exchange between the two currencies of the leg of a deal.
rate.Name: rate

strikeQuoteBasis.Doc: The method by which the strike rate is quoted, in terms of the deposit (principal) and alternate currencies.
strikeQuoteBasis.Name: strikeQuoteBasis
